Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.48,0:23:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(604.8,700)}你们好像很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有些开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
